flowchart LR
  %% Job context architecture
  T[Track name] --> Q[Job query builder]
  L[Location] --> U[Query URL builder]
  Q --> U
  C[.env loader] --> N[Adzuna config\nADZUNA_BASE_URL\nADZUNA_APP_ID\nADZUNA_APP_KEY\nADZUNA_COUNTRY\nADZUNA_CURRENCY]
  N --> U
  U --> H[HTTP request]
  H --> J[JSON response]
  J --> S[Salary range extractor]
  J --> G[Job title extractor]
  J --> O[Company extractor]
  S --> R[CareerContext object]
  G --> R
  O --> R
  R --> D[to_dict output]
  D --> X[Career context output]
